snippet.title: Headquarters: World War II Dev Log #12
snippet.description:
The full release of Headquarters World War II will happen very soon on the 11th of April, and the Dev would like to tell you more about the ongoing release preparations and the latest changes to the game.
If you would like to know more, please follow the link below to access the full dev log article: https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/1840800/view/4174347361794057856 

🎮 Wishlist it on Steam ➡️ http://steam.gs/l/3ptsd
💬 Join the Discord Server ➡️ https://discord.gg/DKp5gqpXsB 
🦎 More info on Slitherine ➡️ https://www.slitherine.com/game/headquarters-world-war-ii
